### Create Admin User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Create Token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Create Type
POST http://localhost:8080/api/type
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}

{
  "name": "Fire",
  "form": { "type": "fire", "sub": { "a": 1 } }
}

### Create occurrence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/occurrence
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}

{
  "usersId": 1,
  "endDate": "2030-12-31",
  "importance": "URGENT",
  "occurrenceType": 1 ,
  "occurrenceInfo": { "location": "Lisbon", "people": [1,2,3] }
}

### SSE for first occurrence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/occurrence/1/listen
Content-Type: application/json

### SSE for list of occurrences
POST http://localhost:8080/api/occurrence/listen
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new occurrence
POST http://localhost:8080/api/occurrence
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_user}}

{
  "usersId": 1,
  "endDate": "2028-12-31",
  "importance": "NORMAL",
  "occurrenceType": { "type": "fire", "sub": { "a": 1 } },
  "occurrenceInfo": { "location": "Lisbon", "people": [1,2,3] }
}

### Delete newly created occurrence
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/occurrence/2
Content-Type: application/json

